<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng guó shǔ yú shàng dì 迦南551</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǎ pà zhǐ yǒu yī dī xuè yī dī hàn, yě yào sǎ zài zhōng guó,
 nǎ pà zhǐ shèng yī kǒu qì yī bǎ lì, yě yào xiàn gěi zhōng guó..
 zhōng guó a yǒu duō shǎo hǎi wài chì zi, wèi nǐ qí dǎo kū qì,
 zhàn zài dà yáng de bǐ àn, shí shí bǎ nǐ zhuāng zài xīn lǐ;
 tīng mǔ qīn chuān yuè hǎi xiá de hū huàn shēng, zhōng guó rén shì shén de ér nǚ.
 zhōng guó a zhōng guó nǐ kuài lái dé ān xī shén yǐ jīng zhǎo dào nǐ;
 nǐ yǐ bù zài mí tú shàng bá shè, zhōng guó shǔ yú shàng dì.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>551</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>